title: Episode 125: The Vagina Whisperer (Feat. Astra and Ashley)
itunes:title: Episode 125: The Vagina Whisperer (Feat. Astra and Ashley)
description:
On this week's episode of Lip Service, on-air personality for 103.5 KTU, Astra, and Ashley, owner of Up Spa in NYC, sit with the ladies and discuss vagacials and vagina maintenance. The ladies also decide what they'd name their sex dolls, and talk about when it's okay to share finances with their partner.
